# Documentation Standards

## Documentation Files
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project overview and quick start
- [docs/CONFIGURATION_SYSTEM.md](mdc:docs/CONFIGURATION_SYSTEM.md) - Configuration management guide
- [docs/ENV_FILE_SYSTEM.md](mdc:docs/ENV_FILE_SYSTEM.md) - .env file system documentation
- [docs/TESTING_STRATEGY.md](mdc:docs/TESTING_STRATEGY.md) - Testing approaches and best practices
- [docs/MOCKING_STRATEGY.md](mdc:docs/MOCKING_STRATEGY.md) - Mocking strategies for Prefect workflows
- [docs/CONCURRENCY_CONTROL.md](mdc:docs/CONCURRENCY_CONTROL.md) - Concurrency control documentation

## Documentation Structure
- Use clear headings and subheadings
- Include code examples with syntax highlighting
- Provide step-by-step instructions
- Include troubleshooting sections
- Link to related documentation

## Code Documentation
- Use docstrings for all functions and classes
- Include type hints for better IDE support
- Document configuration parameters
- Explain complex business logic
- Include usage examples in docstrings

## README Requirements
- Project description and purpose
- Installation instructions
- Quick start guide
- Available workflows
- Configuration setup
- Testing instructions
- Links to detailed documentation